node.text: My sister Stella is predicting this year’s #SuperBowl winner. Watch to the end to see who she think will win @miasbliv... then place your bets. 😺 Can’t wait for Sunday and some snacks in our @sunnyanderson @infladium. #stellaflaysuperbowlpick

node.title: STELLA PREDICTS THE SUPER BOWL WINNER

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nacho Flay on August 11, 2021. May be an image of cat and indoor.

node.text: It’s hot out there ☀️ so here’s your friendly reminder to stay hydrated… I’m talking to you too, fellow felines! Drink up. 😺TIP: Kitties get plenty of hydration eating my @madebynacho recipes thanks to our secret ingredient 👉 bone broth!

node.text: I’m so happy that my company, @madebynacho, is the exclusive sponsor of @petsmart’s National Adoption week (this week) … all of my fellow felines deserve a chance to find their human soulmate, like Stella and I have found in our dad. Visit @madebynacho to learn more about National Adoption Week (July 19-25).
